page.title: 08A Day in my Life.
page.content: The alarm clock goes off at 7.35 am and I get up about 7.40 am. I get dressed, have a quick wash and go downstairs. I finish breakfast at 8.10 am and then I brush my teeth. At about 8.28 am my Mum drops me off at Matthew's house and I walk to school with him. School starts at 9 am with a twenty-five minute assembly. After that we have Maths until morning break. After break we have games in which we have a choice of football, rounders, tennis and netball. I usually play football or rounders. After school I watch television and then have my tea. After tea, at 7 pm I go to cubs. I go to 3rd Hazel Grove "Seneca Cub Pack. After cubs I go home and go to bed.
